PN,32901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,FFunding to restore wildlife will
OL,8,Fsupport 130 projects to safeguard the
OL,9,Ffuture of 364 threatened species, some
OL,10,Fof which are only found in England,
OL,11,Fgovernment nature agency Natural
OL,12,FEngland said.
OL,14,FProjects from using detection dogs to
OL,15,Ffind rare orchids to tracking "forever
OL,16,Fchemicals" in dolphins and protecting
OL,17,Friverside beetles have secured a share
OL,18,Fof #60 million investment in nature.
OL,26,@wD@_OUxD@JO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,FSwallowtail butterflies, white-clawed
OL,8,Fcrayfish, New Forest cicadas, red
OL,9,Fsquirrels, water voles, bats, bees,
OL,10,Fbeavers, wildflowers, nightingales and
OL,11,Fturtle doves are among the wildlife
OL,12,Fthe investment aims to protect.
OL,14,FThe Government funding is part of
OL,15,Fefforts to meet legal targets to halt
OL,16,Fdeclines in nature by 2030, and comes
OL,17,Fin the face of long-term drops in
OL,18,Fwildlife populations which have fallen
OL,19,Fby a third since the 1970s, with one
OL,20,Fin six species at risk of extinction
OL,21,Fin Great Britain.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,FAmong the species set to benefit from
OL,8,Fthe funding are the incredibly-scarce
OL,9,Fghost orchid, which went unrecorded
OL,10,Ffor 23 years before it was
OL,11,Frediscovered in 2009.
OL,13,FNatural England is using detection
OL,14,Fdogs and eDNA technology to locate and
OL,15,Fprotect populations of the rare plant.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,FThe Zoological Society of London (ZSL)
OL,8,Fwill work to quantify the exposure to
OL,9,FPFAS, known as forever chemicals, in
OL,10,Fdolphins and harbour porpoises, while
OL,11,Fa project will track individual
OL,12,Fswallowtail butterflies and map their
OL,13,Fbehaviour and geographic links to the
OL,14,Ffood plant milk-parsley.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,FOther projects include conservation
OL,8,Fwork in Cumbria to protect the
OL,9,Fnorthern dune tiger beetle, efforts to
OL,10,Fsave the brilliantly coloured tansy
OL,11,Fbeetle, whose survival depends on
OL,12,Friverside habitats it shares with
OL,13,Ffarmers, and moves to save white-
OL,14,Fclawed crayfish, at risk from invasive
OL,15,Fspecies.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,FWith farmed landscapes seeing some of
OL,8,Fthe sharpest declines in nature, and
OL,9,Fwith healthy ecosystems essential for
OL,10,Fproductive, resilient agriculture, a
OL,11,Fnumber of projects receiving funding
OL,12,Fwill support farmers and land managers
OL,13,Fto restore nature alongside food
OL,14,Fproduction, Natural England said.
OL,16,FWhat is the reaction from Cumbria?
OL,18,FAs part of the announcement The West
OL,19,FCumbria Rivers Trust has secured #820k
OL,20,Fto deliver river restoration and
OL,21,Ffreshwater pearl mussel recovery work.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,FThe programme combines targeted
OL,8,Fhabitat restoration with species
OL,9,Frecovery work, bringing together WCRT,
OL,10,FEden Rivers Trust, South Cumbria
OL,11,FRivers Trust, the Freshwater
OL,12,FBiological Association (FBA), farmers
OL,13,Fand landowners to deliver practical
OL,14,Fimprovements for river health and
OL,15,Fbiodiversity.
OL,17,FPlanned work includes floodplain
OL,18,Frestoration, embankment lowering,
OL,19,Friverbank improvements and measures to
OL,20,Freduce sediment entering rivers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,FChris West, Project Manager for West
OL,8,FCumbria Rivers Trust said:
OL,10,F"This funding is a significant boost
OL,11,Ffor river restoration work across
OL,12,FCumbria. While freshwater pearl
OL,13,Fmussels are at the heart of the
OL,14,Fprogramme, the benefits will be much
OL,15,Fwider, improving river habitat, water
OL,16,Fquality and resilience for a whole
OL,17,Frange of wildlife.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,F"It also strengthens long-term
OL,8,Fpartnership working across catchments,
OL,9,Fwhich is essential if we are to
OL,10,Frestore and protect Freshwater Pearl
OL,11,FMussels."
OL,13,FLouise Lavictoire, Head of Science for
OL,14,FFBA said: "The FBA are so excited to
OL,15,Fbe working once again with WCRT and
OL,16,Fpartners, building upon our solid
OL,17,Ffoundations of evidence-based
OL,18,Frestoration.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,F"In our most ambitious target to date,
OL,8,Fwe plan on reinforcing struggling
OL,9,Fmussel populations with over 9,000
OL,10,Fjuveniles, pulling populations back
OL,11,Ffrom the brink of extinction."
OL,13,FAnd "native species recovery hubs",
OL,14,Fled by Biaza zoos and aquariums and
OL,15,Ftheir partners, will spearhead
OL,16,Fbreeding-for-release programmes,
OL,17,Fsupporting the recovery of 16 rare
OL,18,Finvertebrate species, officials said.
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@bO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,FThe #60 million funding is part of the
OL,8,FGovernment's "wild again: restoring
OL,9,FEngland's wildlife" initiative to
OL,10,Frestore nature in the country, and
OL,11,Fwill be invested by the Environment
OL,12,FDepartment over the next three years.
OL,14,FA further #30 million from the
OL,15,FGovernment will be dedicated to
OL,16,Fhelping species recover on the
OL,17,Fnational forest estate.
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@SO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,FEnvironment Secretary Emma Reynolds
OL,8,Fsaid: "Nearly one in six species in
OL,9,FBritain are threatened with extinction
OL,10,Fand this Government is taking action
OL,11,Fto reverse that decline.
OL,13,F"Through the largest-ever investment
OL,14,Fin species recovery, we are backing
OL,15,Fprojects across the country to protect
OL,16,Fthreatened wildlife, restore habitats
OL,17,Fand secure the future of some of
OL,18,FEngland's most iconic species."
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,FNatural England chairman Tony Juniper
OL,8,Fsaid the agency's species recovery
OL,9,Fwork over decades had revealed how
OL,10,F"even the rarest of the rare" could be
OL,11,Fbrought back from the brink of
OL,12,Fextinction.
OL,14,F"The red kite, lady's slipper orchid,
OL,15,Fpool frog, beaver and large blue
OL,16,Fbutterfly are among examples that
OL,17,Fdemonstrate the many opportunities at
OL,18,Fhand and what can be achieved for
OL,19,Fnature and wider society.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@]O]vD@AOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/14
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,330,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F329A1783705757
OL,3,CThreatened birds, butterflies and
OL,4,Cflowers get share of #60m to restore
OL,5,Cnature
OL,7,F"We know that good science and
OL,8,Feffective partnerships can help
OL,9,Frestore species to favourable status,
OL,10,Fand this funding will enable us to
OL,11,Fsupport many initiatives to help halt
OL,12,Fand reverse the decline of our
OL,13,Fwonderful wildlife."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
OL,26,@oD@AOU
